title: Menage a 3 (Web Comic) - Books 1 through 6 {WebComixFan}
description:
"MENAGE A 3" Web Comic

"Menage a 3" (ma3comic.com) by Gisele "Giz" Lagace and Dave "Dave Zero" Lumsdon, follows the lives and adventures of three roommates in their attempts to find love, success and the pleasures of life.  It is consistently rated amongst the top 50 webcomics annually and has enjoyed success in print in addition to online.  The strip features frequent nudity and sex, and is quite definitely NSFW.

This torrent includes books 1 through 6 of "Menage a 3" in CBR format.  This represents the first six years of the strip's run, from May 2008 through June 2014.  Though the breakdown matches that of the published volumes, note that these are NOT scans of the books; all the comics in this torrent were downloaded directly from the ma3comic.com Web site
